title: The Housemaid Wants to be in Higher Position - Novel Updates
tags: Ancient China   Aristocracy   Beautiful Female Lead   Butlers   Character Growth   Child Protagonist   Clever Protagonist   Couple Growth   Cute Protagonist   Different Social Status   Family   Female Protagonist   Maids   Master-Servant Relationship   Nobles   Poor Protagonist   Second Chance   S*ave Protagonist   S*aves   Weak to Strong
author: 紫苏琉莲
description: This is the story of a noble daughter of a favorable aristocratic family. When disaster came, in one day, the whole family became slaves. In order to protect her beloved relatives, Shen Xiangwan had to use all sorts of tricks to flatter the master and bribe the slaves to secure a place in the back house. All aspects of her life were going smoothly until the young master, who had been struggling to help her to the top, suddenly changed his style and began to find ways to lure her to the couch.>
